&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Take refuge at Mandarin Oriental Hotel Group and discover some of the most exquisite hotels and resorts in the world. &nbsp;Unwind at a meditative spa, indulge in the finest dining or recharge in a culturally-vibrant capital. Each destination brings &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;celebrated comfort and legendary service. Whether you&rsquo;re longing for the indulgence of a poolside retreat, the bustle of a major metropolis or the relaxation of a world-class spa, Mandarin Oriental hotels and resorts offer that perfect retreat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;A stunning resort overlooking the Aegean Sea, Mandarin Oriental, Bodrum is where dreams come true. A luxury 5-star hotel retreat with two private beaches and excellent leisure facilities, we invite you to lie back, relax and savour the moment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Diners Club cardmembers enjoy&nbsp;extra special recognition throughout their stay with valuable benefits including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Upgrade upon availability (room to room, suite to suite)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Welcome amenity &ndash; seasonal amenities that vary throughout the year&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Continental breakfast for two on each morning during the stay&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Complimentary Internet access&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;USD50 dining or spa service credit for Suite reservations only (one-time per stay)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Early check-in, based on availability&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Reserve your room online,&nbsp;call Mandarin Oriental Central Reservations&nbsp;or call the hotel directly. When booking, enter&nbsp;code &ldquo;DINCLB&rdquo; in the &lsquo;Corporate/Promo Code&rsquo; field or provide the code to a phone agent.&nbsp;Click here for or more information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Offer is subject to availability, blackout dates may apply and advance booking is required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Offer is valid on select room categories and is not valid for group bookings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other offers or promotions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/p&gt;
